snippet.title: Cruis'n Blast - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
The arcade phenomenon Cruis'n Blast is now available on Nintendo Switch! The fourth installment in the iconic racing series features 29 thrilling tracks, 23 customizable vehicles and support for up to four players! 

Purchase Cruis'n Blast now on Nintendo eShop and at select retail locations: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/cruisn-blast-switch/.
